summary: Two-part Green Cave located in the Reach. Designed for Mid- to High-level characters.
descriptionHtml: Granhurst Cave is located near Purewater Run, south of Markarth. It\'s split into two areas. The first one is full of wild cave animals like bears and trolls and spiders, and the second area holds an abandoned Dwarven settlement, populated with Dwarven mechanisms and Falmer. It\'s designed for mid-high level characters, so enter at your own risk and watch your back.
author: Aaron Mark
